					<!-- Live mode input display (P8d). Edit control removed:
					     bidirectional sync from RunScript helper crashes Kodi,
					     and the QWERTY's focus-on-keys model wants a virtual
					     cursor anyway. Background image carries the textbox
					     visual; the property altus.search.input.display holds
